{"type":"message","id":"8496c286","parentId":"a73cbb79","timestamp":"2026-03-30T12:15:29.426Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0oc61kGrLbPLQp3Ul5ShahIE","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Search: site:bls.gov OR site:federalreserve.gov OR site:bea.gov CPI PPI nonfarm payroll unemployment rate PCE FOMC Powell speech next 3 days\n**Engine**: tavily\n\n### Answer\n\nThe Federal Reserve Board announced it has made the joint findings with the Office of the Comptroller of the Currency required for the OCC to approve a request by Morgan Stanley Bank, N.A., for an exemption under section 23A of the Federal Reserve Act. This decision was made on 30/03/2026 at 5:00 p.m. EDT. There is no mention of CPI, PPI, nonfarm payroll, unemployment rate, PCE, FOMC, or Powell's speech in the provided data.\n\n---\n\n### Results (1)\n\n- **Federal Reserve Board announces it has made the joint findings with the Office of the Comptroller of the Currency required for the OCC to approve a request by Morgan Stanley Bank, N.A., for an exemption under section 23A of the Federal Reserve Act - Federal Reserve Board (.gov)** (0%)\n  https://www.federalreserve.gov/newsevents/pressreleases/orders20260326a.htm\n  A **.gov** website belongs to an official government organization in the United States. Back to Home Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System. # Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System. ### Federal Reserve Board announces it has made the joint findings with the Office of the Comptroller of the Currency required for the OCC to approve a request by Morgan Stanley Bank, N.A., for an ..."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6948,"aggregated":"## Search: site:bls.gov OR site:federalreserve.gov OR site:bea.gov CPI PPI nonfarm payroll unemployment rate PCE FOMC Powell speech next 3 days\n**Engine**: tavily\n\n### Answer\n\nThe Federal Reserve Board announced it has made the joint findings with the Office of the Comptroller